Let <M>B_1,B_2\in \beta.</M>  Then <M>B_i = K_i^c.</M>  for some closed and compact <M>K_i.</M>  

Hence <M>B_1\cap B_2 = (K_1\cup K_2)^c = K^c,</M>  where <M>K=K_1\cup K_2</M>  is closed and compact. 

Hence <M>B_1\cap B_2\in \beta.</M>  So <M>\beta</M>  is a basis.

